longBusinessSummary: Global Hemp Group Inc. focuses on the industrial hemp industry in Canada and the United States. The company was formerly known as Arris Holdings Inc. and changed its name to Global Hemp Group Inc. in March 2014. Global Hemp Group Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in North Vancouver, Canada.
